<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>송우고2 2025 3월모의고사 시험범위 | Witheun by.은서쌤</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net">
<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard@v1.3.9/dist/web/variable/pretendardvariable-dynamic-subset.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
   Toss.tech 스타일 디자인 시스템
   배경 흰색, 타이포 중심, 미니멀 플랫
═══════════════════════════════════════════════ */
:root {
  --g900:#111827; --g800:#1F2937; --g700:#374151; --g600:#4B5563;
  --g500:#6B7280; --g400:#9CA3AF; --g300:#D1D5DB; --g200:#E5E7EB;
  --g100:#F3F4F6; --g50:#F9FAFB; --w:#FFFFFF;

  --blue:#3182F6;  --blue-bg:#EFF6FF;  --blue-mid:#DBEAFE;
  --green:#16A34A; --green-bg:#F0FDF4; --green-mid:#DCFCE7;
  --red:#DC2626;   --red-bg:#FEF2F2;   --red-mid:#FEE2E2;
  --orange:#EA580C;--orange-bg:#FFF7ED;
  --purple:#7C3AED;--purple-bg:#F5F3FF;
  --yellow:#CA8A04;--yellow-bg:#FEFCE8;--yellow-mid:#FEF9C3;
  --teal:#0891B2;  --teal-bg:#ECFEFF;

  --radius-sm:6px; --radius-md:10px; --radius-lg:14px;
  --shadow-sm:0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.05);
  --shadow-md:0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.06);
}

/* ── Reset & Base ── */
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
body{
  font-family:'Pretendard Variable',Pretendard,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,
    'Segoe UI',system-ui,sans-serif;
  font-size:15px;letter-spacing:-0.4px;line-height:1.75;
  background:#ffffff;color:var(--g900);
  -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
}

/* ── 레이아웃 ── */
.wrap{max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 20px 96px;}

/* ═══════════════════════════════
   HEADER
═══════════════════════════════ */
.top-header{
  padding:48px 0 28px;
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--g200);
  margin-bottom:0;
}
.top-header h1{
  font-size:26px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.8px;
  color:var(--g900);line-height:1.3;margin-bottom:6px;
}
.top-header .sub{
  font-size:14px;color:var(--g500);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-0.2px;
}

/* ═══════════════════════════════
   TAB NAV — pill
═══════════════════════════════ */
.pill-nav{
  display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:6px;
  position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;
  background:#fff;
  padding:14px 0 12px;
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--g200);
  margin-bottom:32px;
}
.pill{
  height:32px;padding:0 14px;border-radius:100px;
  font-size:13px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:-0.2px;
  border:1.5px solid var(--g200);
  background:#fff;color:var(--g500);
  cursor:pointer;transition:all .18s ease;
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;
}
.pill:hover{border-color:var(--blue);color:var(--blue);background:var(--blue-bg);}
.pill.active{
  background:var(--g900);color:#fff;
  border-color:var(--g900);
}

/* ═══════════════════════════════
   PANEL 전환 애니메이션
═══════════════════════════════ */
.q-panel{display:none;animation:fadeUp .25s ease;}
.q-panel.active{display:block;}
@keyframes fadeUp{
  from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(10px)}
  to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}
}

/* ─── Q 카드 ─── */
.q-card{
  background:#fff;
  border:1px solid var(--g200);
  border-radius:var(--radius-lg);
  padding:28px 24px;
  margin-bottom:16px;
}

/* ─── Q 타이틀 헤더 ─── */
.q-title{
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;
  padding-bottom:16px;
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--g100);
  margin-bottom:20px;
}
.q-num{
  font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.5px;
  background:var(--g900);color:#fff;
  padding:3px 10px;border-radius:100px;
  flex-shrink:0;
}
.q-type{
  font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--g700);
  line-height:1.4;letter-spacing:-0.2px;
}
.q-type-tag{
  font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.2px;
  padding:3px 8px;border-radius:100px;
  margin-left:auto;flex-shrink:0;
  text-transform:uppercase;
}
.q-type-tag.claim  {background:var(--blue-mid);  color:var(--blue);}
.q-type-tag.meaning{background:var(--purple-bg); color:var(--purple);}
.q-type-tag.gist   {background:var(--orange-bg); color:var(--orange);}
.q-type-tag.title  {background:var(--green-mid); color:var(--green);}
.q-type-tag.tf     {background:var(--orange-bg); color:var(--orange);}
.q-type-tag.vocab  {background:var(--red-mid);   color:var(--red);}
.q-type-tag.blank  {background:var(--teal-bg);   color:var(--teal);}
.q-type-tag.order  {background:var(--yellow-mid);color:var(--yellow);}
.q-type-tag.insert {background:var(--purple-bg); color:var(--purple);}
.q-type-tag.flow   {background:var(--orange-bg); color:var(--orange);}
.q-type-tag.summary{background:var(--teal-bg);   color:var(--teal);}

/* ═══════════════════════════════
   문장 카드 — 심플 left-border
═══════════════════════════════ */
.sent{
  padding:14px 16px;
  margin-bottom:10px;
  border-left:2px solid var(--g200);
  background:#fff;
  border-radius:0 var(--radius-sm) var(--radius-sm) 0;
  transition:border-color .15s;
}
.sent:hover{border-left-color:var(--g400);}
.sent.key-sent{
  border-left:2px solid var(--yellow);
  background:var(--yellow-bg);
  border-radius:0 var(--radius-sm) var(--radius-sm) 0;
}
.sent.wrong-sent{
  border-left:2px solid var(--red);
  background:var(--red-bg);
}

.sent-num{
  font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.3px;
  color:var(--g400);text-transform:uppercase;
  margin-bottom:6px;
}

.eng-line{
  font-size:15px;font-weight:500;color:var(--g900);
  line-height:1.85;margin-bottom:12px;
  word-break:keep-all;
}
.eng-line u{
  text-decoration-color:var(--red);
  text-underline-offset:3px;
  text-decoration-thickness:1.5px;
}

/* ─── 의미구 분석 박스 ─── */
.parse-box{
  background:var(--g50);
  border:1px solid var(--g100);
  border-radius:var(--radius-md);
  padding:10px 14px;
  margin-bottom:10px;
}
.phrase{
  display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:7px;
  padding:3px 0;font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;
}
.plabel{
  display:inline-block;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;
  letter-spacing:.3px;padding:1px 7px;
  border-radius:100px;flex-shrink:0;
  min-width:30px;text-align:center;
}
.plabel.subj{background:var(--blue-mid);  color:var(--blue);}
.plabel.verb{background:var(--red-mid);   color:var(--red);}
.plabel.obj {background:var(--green-mid); color:var(--green);}
.plabel.comp{background:var(--orange-bg); color:var(--orange);}
.plabel.mod {background:var(--g100);      color:var(--g500);}
.plabel.conj{background:var(--purple-bg); color:var(--purple);}
.peng{color:var(--g800);font-weight:500;}
.pkor{color:var(--g500);font-size:12px;}

/* ─── 문법 노트 ─── */
.grammar-note{
  display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:6px;flex-wrap:wrap;
  background:var(--blue-bg);
  border-radius:var(--radius-sm);
  padding:10px 14px;
  margin-bottom:10px;
  font-size:13px;color:var(--g700);line-height:1.7;
}
.gn-tag{
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;
  font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.3px;
  padding:2px 8px;border-radius:100px;
  flex-shrink:0;
}
.gn-tag.grammar  {background:var(--blue);  color:#fff;}
.gn-tag.blank    {background:var(--teal);  color:#fff;}
.gn-tag.vocab-tag{background:var(--green); color:#fff;}

/* ─── 어휘 배지 ─── */
.vocab-badges{
  display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:5px;margin-bottom:10px;
}
.badge{
  font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:-0.1px;
  padding:3px 10px;border-radius:100px;
}
.badge.syn  {background:var(--green-bg);color:var(--green);}
.badge.ant  {background:var(--red-bg);  color:var(--red);}
.badge.key  {background:var(--blue-bg); color:var(--blue);}
.badge.wrong{background:var(--red-mid); color:var(--red);}

/* ─── 한국어 해석 ─── */
.kor-line{
  font-size:13px;color:var(--g500);line-height:1.75;
  padding:6px 0 0 12px;
  border-left:2px solid var(--g200);
}

/* ─── 선택지 ─── */
.choices{
  background:var(--g50);
  border:1px solid var(--g100);
  border-radius:var(--radius-md);
  padding:14px 18px;
  margin-bottom:14px;
}
.choice{
  display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px;
  padding:5px 0;font-size:13.5px;line-height:1.6;
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--g100);
  color:var(--g700);
}
.choice:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
.choice .cnum{font-weight:700;color:var(--g400);min-width:16px;flex-shrink:0;}
.choice.correct{color:var(--blue);font-weight:700;}
.choice.correct .cnum{color:var(--blue);}
.choice.wrong-ans{color:var(--red);}
.choice.wrong-ans .cnum{color:var(--red);}

/* ─── 요약 박스 ─── */
.summary-box{
  background:#fff;
  border:1px solid var(--g200);
  border-top:2px solid var(--g900);
  border-radius:0 0 var(--radius-md) var(--radius-md);
  padding:18px 20px;
  margin-top:20px;
}
.sum-item{
  padding:10px 0;
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--g100);
  font-size:13px;line-height:1.75;
}
.sum-item:last-child{border-bottom:none;padding-bottom:0;}
.sum-label{
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;
  font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.3px;
  padding:2px 9px;border-radius:100px;
  margin-bottom:5px;text-transform:uppercase;
}
.sum-label.logic {background:var(--yellow-mid);color:var(--yellow);}
.sum-label.answer{background:var(--blue-mid);  color:var(--blue);}
.sum-label.wrong {background:var(--red-mid);   color:var(--red);}
.sum-label.voca  {background:var(--green-mid); color:var(--green);}
.sum-content{color:var(--g600);}

/* ─── 순서 배열 ─── */
.order-flow{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;padding:14px 18px;margin-bottom:14px;background:var(--blue-bg);border:1px solid var(--blue-mid);border-radius:var(--radius-md);font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--blue);}
.order-flow .arrow{color:var(--g400);font-weight:400;}
.section-label{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--g400);letter-spacing:.5px;margin:20px 0 8px;}

/* ─── 요약문 ─── */
.summary-sentence{background:var(--blue-bg);border:1px solid var(--blue-mid);border-radius:var(--radius-md);padding:16px 20px;margin-bottom:14px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;color:var(--g800);}
.summary-sentence .blank{background:var(--green-mid);padding:2px 8px;border-radius:100px;font-weight:700;color:var(--green);}

/* ─── 바닥글 ─── */
.footer{
  text-align:center;
  padding:32px 0 24px;
  margin-top:48px;
  border-top:1px solid var(--g200);
}
.footer .brand{
  font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:var(--g900);
  letter-spacing:-0.4px;margin-bottom:4px;
}
.footer .by{font-size:13px;color:var(--g400);font-weight:500;}

/* ─── 반응형 ─── */
@media(max-width:520px){
  .wrap{padding:0 14px 72px;}
  .q-card{padding:20px 16px;}
  .top-header{padding:32px 0 20px;}
  .top-header h1{font-size:21px;}
  .eng-line{font-size:14.5px;}
  .pill{height:30px;padding:0 12px;font-size:12px;}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">

<!-- ═══ 헤더 ═══ -->
<div class="top-header">
  <h1>송우고2 2025 3월모의고사 시험범위</h1>
  <div class="sub">Witheun by.은서쌤</div>
</div>

<!-- ═══ 탭 네비게이션 ═══ -->
<div class="pill-nav" id="pillNav">
  <span class="pill active" data-q="q20">20</span>
  <span class="pill" data-q="q21">21</span>
  <span class="pill" data-q="q22">22</span>
  <span class="pill" data-q="q24">24</span>
  <span class="pill" data-q="q37">37</span>
  <span class="pill" data-q="q40">40</span>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- Q20 주장 파악 -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="q-panel active" id="q20">
<div class="q-card">
  <div class="q-title">
    <span class="q-num">20</span>
    <span class="q-type">다음 글에서 필자가 주장하는 바로 가장 적절한 것은?</span>
    <span class="q-type-tag claim">주장</span>
  </div>

  <div class="sent key-sent">
    <div class="sent-num">01 ★ 주제문</div>
    <div class="eng-line">Fans who are inclined to spend a lot of time thinking about what athletes owe them as fans should also think about the corresponding obligations that fans might have <em>as fans</em>.</div>
    <div class="parse-box">
      <div class="phrase"><span class="plabel subj">S</span><span class="peng">Fans who are inclined to spend a lot of time thinking about what athletes owe them as fans</span><span class="pkor">팬으로서 선수가 자신에게 무엇을 해주어야 하는지 생각하는 데 많은 시간을 쓰는 경향이 있는 팬들은</span></div>
      <div class="phrase"><span class="plabel verb">V</span><span class="peng">should also think about</span><span class="pkor">~에 대해서도 생각해야 한다</span></div>
      <div class="phrase"><span class="plabel obj">O</span><span class="peng">the corresponding obligations that fans might have as fans</span><span class="pkor">팬으로서 가질 수 있는 상응하는 의무</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="grammar-note">
      <span class="gn-tag grammar">★어법</span>
      <strong>관계대명사 who</strong>: Fans를 수식. <strong>what athletes owe them</strong>: owe A B 구문에서 what이 B 역할(선수가 그들에게 빚진 것). <strong>corresponding</strong>: 상응하는 — 핵심 키워드.
    </div>
    <div class="vocab-badges">
      <span class="badge key">be inclined to ~하는 경향이 있다</span>
      <span class="badge key">corresponding 상응하는</span>
      <span class="badge key">obligation 의무, 책임</span>
    </div>
    <div class="kor-line">선수가 팬인 자신에게 무엇을 빚지고 있는지 생각하는 데 많은 시간을 쏟는 경향이 있는 팬들은, 팬으로서 자신이 가질 수 있는 상응하는 의무에 대해서도 생각해 보아야 한다.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="sent">
    <div class="sent-num">02</div>
    <div class="eng-line">One who thinks only about what they are entitled to receive from their friends without ever giving a moment's thought to what they owe their friends is, to put it mildly, not a very good friend.</div>
    <div class="parse-box">
      <div class="phrase"><span class="plabel subj">S</span><span class="peng">One who thinks only about what they are entitled to receive from their friends</span><span class="pkor">친구로부터 받을 자격이 있는 것만 생각하는 사람은</span></div>
      <div class="phrase"><span class="plabel mod">부사구</span><span class="peng">without ever giving a moment's thought to what they owe their friends</span><span class="pkor">친구에게 빚진 것에 잠시도 생각하지 않고</span></div>
      <div class="phrase"><span class="plabel verb">V</span><span class="peng">is</span><span class="pkor">~이다</span></div>
      <div class="phrase"><span class="plabel mod">삽입구</span><span class="peng">to put it mildly,</span><span class="pkor">부드럽게 말하자면,</span></div>
      <div class="phrase"><span class="plabel comp">C</span><span class="peng">not a very good friend</span><span class="pkor">그다지 좋은 친구가 아닌</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="grammar-note">
      <span class="gn-tag grammar">★어법</span>
      <strong>be entitled to + V</strong>: ~할 자격이 있다. <strong>without + V-ing</strong>: ~하지 않고 (부정의 부대상황). <strong>to put it mildly</strong>: 부드럽게 말하면 (삽입구).<br>
      💡 <strong>without V-ing 풀어쓰기</strong>: without ever giving a moment's thought to... = <em>and they never give a moment's thought to what they owe their friends</em> (그리고 그들은 친구에게 빚진 것에 대해 잠시도 생각하지 않는다).
    </div>
    <div class="vocab-badges">
      <span class="badge key">be entitled to ~할 자격이 있다</span>
      <span class="badge key">to put it mildly 부드럽게 말하면</span>
      <span class="badge key">give a thought to ~에 대해 생각하다</span>
    </div>
    <div class="kor-line">자신이 친구로부터 받을 자격이 있는 것에 대해서만 생각하고 친구에게 빚진 것에 대해서는 잠시도 생각하지 않는 사람은, 부드럽게 말하면, 그다지 좋은 친구가 아니다.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="sent">
    <div class="sent-num">03</div>
    <div class="eng-line">Similarly, fans who only think about what athletes owe them without ever thinking about what they owe to athletes have failed to take the fan/athlete relationship all that seriously.</div>
    <div class="parse-box">
      <div class="phrase"><span class="plabel conj">접속</span><span class="peng">Similarly,</span><span class="pkor">마찬가지로,</span></div>
      <div class="phrase"><span class="plabel subj">S</span><span class="peng">fans who only think about what athletes owe them</span><span class="pkor">선수가 자신에게 빚진 것만 생각하는 팬들은</span></div>
      <div class="phrase"><span class="plabel mod">부사구</span><span class="peng">without ever thinking about what they owe to athletes</span><span class="pkor">선수에게 빚진 것에 대해서는 전혀 생각하지 않으면서</span></div>
      <div class="phrase"><span class="plabel verb">V</span><span class="peng">have failed to take</span><span class="pkor">~을 진지하게 받아들이지 못한 것이다</span></div>
      <div class="phrase"><span class="plabel obj">O</span><span class="peng">the fan/athlete relationship all that seriously</span><span class="pkor">팬/선수 관계를 그만큼 진지하게</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="grammar-note">
      <span class="gn-tag grammar">★어법</span>
      <strong>Similarly</strong>: 친구 관계 비유 → 팬/선수 관계로 전환. <strong>have failed to V</strong>: ~하는 데 실패했다 (현재완료). <strong>all that</strong>: 그만큼, 그렇게 (강조).<br>
      💡 <strong>without V-ing 풀어쓰기</strong>: without ever thinking about... = <em>but they never think about what they owe to athletes</em> (하지만 그들은 선수에게 빚진 것에 대해서는 전혀 생각하지 않는다).
    </div>
    <div class="kor-line">마찬가지로, 선수가 자신에게 빚진 것에 대해서만 생각하고 자신이 선수에게 빚진 것에 대해서는 전혀 생각하지 않는 팬들은 팬/선수 관계를 그만큼 진지하게 받아들이지 못한 것이다.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="sent key-sent">
    <div class="sent-num">04 ★ 결론</div>
    <div class="eng-line">As in nearly every other area of human life, whatever special rights fans may possess are limited by a corresponding set of obligations, and fans who never think about how they can be better fans even as they confidently opine about what athletes owe them are hardly fulfilling their end of the bargain.</div>
    <div class="parse-box">
