      <div class="phrase"><span class="plabel conj">접속</span><span class="peng">and</span><span class="pkor">그리고</span></div>
      <div class="phrase"><span class="plabel subj">S₂</span><span class="peng">fans who never think about how they can be better fans</span><span class="pkor">어떻게 더 나은 팬이 될 수 있는지 결코 생각하지 않는 팬들은</span></div>
      <div class="phrase"><span class="plabel mod">양보절</span><span class="peng">even as they confidently opine about what athletes owe them</span><span class="pkor">선수가 자신에게 빚진 것에 대해 자신 있게 의견을 말하면서도</span></div>
      <div class="phrase"><span class="plabel verb">V₂</span><span class="peng">are hardly fulfilling</span><span class="pkor">거의 이행하지 못하고 있다</span></div>
      <div class="phrase"><span class="plabel obj">O</span><span class="peng">their end of the bargain</span><span class="pkor">거래에서 자신의 몫을</span></div>
