  <div class="sent key-sent">
    <div class="sent-num">02 ★ 핵심 개념</div>
    <div class="eng-line">The garden is a small ecosystem that the grower attempts to keep in a specific state, namely the maximization of fruit and vegetable production.</div>
    <div class="parse-box">
