      <div class="phrase"><span class="plabel comp">C</span><span class="peng">a small ecosystem that the grower attempts to keep in a specific state</span><span class="pkor">재배자가 특정 상태로 유지하려고 애쓰는 작은 생태계</span></div>
      <div class="phrase"><span class="plabel mod">동격</span><span class="peng">namely the maximization of fruit and vegetable production</span><span class="pkor">즉, 과일과 채소 생산의 극대화</span></div>
