    <div class="kor-line">텃밭은 재배자가 특정 상태, 즉 과일과 채소 생산의 극대화를 유지하려고 애쓰는 작은 생태계이다.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="sent">
    <div class="sent-num">03</div>
    <div class="eng-line">To achieve this, the grower is almost always intervening in the dynamics of the ecosystem; they remove unwanted plants that begin to grow and perhaps spray insecticides and fence off the patch to stop insects and other animals from consuming the vegetables.</div>
