      <div class="phrase"><span class="plabel mod">세미콜론 후 부연</span><span class="peng">they remove unwanted plants... and perhaps spray insecticides and fence off the patch</span><span class="pkor">원치 않는 식물을 제거하고, 살충제를 뿌리며, 울타리를 쳐서</span></div>
