  <div class="sent key-sent">
    <div class="sent-num">04 ★ 밑줄 문장</div>
    <div class="eng-line">Since maximizing vegetable growth is an inherently unstable state for the ecosystem, the grower is effectively <u>keeping the ball on a slope</u>.</div>
