      <div class="phrase"><span class="plabel verb">V</span><span class="peng">has been addressed</span><span class="pkor">다루어져 왔다</span></div>
      <div class="phrase"><span class="plabel mod">전치사구</span><span class="peng">through humour</span><span class="pkor">유머를 통해</span></div>
      <div class="phrase"><span class="plabel mod">관계절</span><span class="peng">in a way that has helped to make more progressive values more acceptable than previously</span><span class="pkor">보다 진보적인 가치를 이전보다 더 수용 가능하게 만드는 데 도움이 된 방식으로</span></div>
