      <div class="phrase"><span class="plabel subj">S</span><span class="peng">a character, usually someone marked as a bigot,</span><span class="pkor">한 인물, 보통 편견이 심한 사람으로 묘사된 누군가가,</span></div>
      <div class="phrase"><span class="plabel verb">V₁</span><span class="peng">resisted</span><span class="pkor">저항하고</span></div>
      <div class="phrase"><span class="plabel obj">O</span><span class="peng">one or more of these developments</span><span class="pkor">이러한 발전 중 하나 이상에</span></div>
