  </div>

  <div class="sent">
    <div class="sent-num">(B)-2</div>
    <div class="eng-line">But chronic stress can confuse the hippocampus and lead to turning signals for cortisol "on" instead of "off," which can trap you in a constant state of fight, flight, or freeze.</div>
    <div class="parse-box">
